    <!-- ================= ABOUT-US SECTION ================= -->
    <section class="about-us-wrapper">
        <div class="about-us-overlay">
            <section class="about-us">
                <h1>KNOW ABOUT US</h1>

                <p class="intro">
                    We are a non-profit organization (NPO) in South Africa with a Public Benefit Organization status and Section 18A tax-exempt status.
                    Established in 1999, Lungisa is dedicated to addressing the healthcare and psychosocial needs of vulnerable communities, with a particular focus on children and youth.
                    Guided by the Sustainable Development Goals, particularly Goal 3, Lungisa strives to ensure healthy lives and promote well-being for all ages.
                </p>

                <!-- ================= MISSION AND VISION ================= -->
                <div class="vision-mission">
                    <div class="mission">
                        <h2>OUR MISSION</h2>
                        <p>To provide quality healthcare and psychosocial services, enhance knowledge and skills among vulnerable community members.</p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="vision">
                        <h2>OUR VISION</h2>
                        <p>To cultivate a community characterized by:</p>
                        <ul>
                            <li>High-quality physical well-being</li>
                            <li>Psychosocial awareness</li>
                            <li>Healthy cultural practices</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>
        </div>

        <!-- ================= VALUES ================= -->
        <div class="values">
            <h2>Organizational Values</h2>
            <p>Lungisa's work is guided by the following core values:</p>

            <ul>
                <!-- Accessibility -->
                <li>
                    <div class="title-row">
                        <strong>Accessibility</strong>
                        <img src="~/Content/Images/accessibility.png" alt="">
                    </div>
                    Ensuring that the community has access to the services provided by Lungisa and to available services.
                </li>

                <!-- Respect -->
                <li>
                    <div class="title-row">
                        <strong>Respect</strong> 
                        <img src="~/Content/Images/respect.png" alt="">
                    </div>
                    Treating all clients with respect and practice inclusiveness in our organisation and the community.
                </li>

                <!-- Confidentiality -->
                <li>
                    <div class="title-row">
                        <strong>Confidentiality</strong>
                        <img src="~/Content/Images/confidential.png" alt="">
                    </div>
                    All information that is brought to our attention will be kept confidentially and will not be unduly exposed.
                </li>

                <!-- Integrity -->
                <li>
                    <div class="title-row">
                        <strong>Integrity</strong>
                        <img src="~/Content/Images/Integrity.png" alt="">
                    </div>
                    We aspire to live to the highest standards of honesty and never compromise the reputation of our organisation and/or our partners, sponsors and supporters.
                </li>

                <!-- Quality Service -->
                <li>
                    <div class="title-row">
                        <strong>Quality Service</strong>
                        <img src="~/Content/Images/QualityService.png" alt="">
                    </div>
                    We are committed to putting our client's needs first, be courteous and rendering services of a high quality.
                </li>
            </ul>
        </div>
